{'id': 5163662, 'body': "Hello there! 

We often post ads around the subject of brain training and riddles on social media channels. This is because our games are often too complicated to be featured in ads so we use riddles and brain training exercises instead.

We're sorry to hear that wasn't clear. We do aim to give an accurate overview of the games we offer when you first install the app, which is why we take you through an assessment test that displays some of the games we have available.", 'modified': '2018-09-21T15:18:22Z'}

